=== 6. GET trace level
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 75
Content-Type: application/xml
Date: REGEX(.*)

<?xml version="1.0"?>
<orion>
  <log>
    <tracelevels>19, 21-25</tracelevels>
  </log>
